<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="faith-n">faith <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /feɪθ/    美 /feɪθ/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1-u">1.★ <strong>[U] 信任；信心：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I'm delighted to know you <strong>have</strong> such <strong>faith in</strong> me.
知道你如此信任我，我很高兴。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Faith can move mountains.
精诚所至，金石为开。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Yeats <strong>had</strong> strong <strong>faith in</strong> the coming of new artistic movements.
叶芝对新艺术运动的未来充满信心。</p><footer>2011 重庆</footer></div>

<h4 id="2-u-c">2.★ <strong>[U] 宗教信仰；[C] 宗教：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>people of different faiths
信仰不同宗教的人士</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">派生词汇</h2>
<p>faithful /'feɪθfl/ adj <br />
faithfully /'feɪθfəli/ adv   </p></div>